#. BetterReef.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.UNDERWATERVENT.DESC
msgctxt "BetterReef.STRINGS.CREATURES.SPECIES.GEYSER.UNDERWATERVENT.DESC"
msgid "A subaquatic fissure that allows high-pressure <link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">Gas</link> to escape from the planet's crust.\n\nBlockages caused by built-up <link=\"ELEMENTSSOLID\">Solid</link> can be removed using a <link=\"UNDERWATERVENTDRILL\">Marine Drill</link>."
msgstr "一道水下裂缝，允许高压<link=\"ELEMENTSGAS\">气体</link>从星球地壳中逸出。\n\n由<link=\"ELEMENTSSOLID\">固体</link>堆积引起的堵塞可使用<link=\"UNDERWATERVENTDRILL\">海洋钻机</link>移除。"

#. BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBLOCKED.TOOLTIP
msgctxt "BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBLOCKED.TOOLTIP"
msgid "This geyser is blocked by <style=\"KKeyword\">{ELEMENT}</style> build-up\n\nIt will resume function when unblocked by a <style=\"KKeyword\">Marine Drill</style>"
msgstr "这个间歇泉被<style=\"KKeyword\">{ELEMENT}</style>堆积阻挡\n\n在由<style=\"KKeyword\">海洋钻机</style>疏通后恢复运作"

#. BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBUILDUPPROGRESS.NAME
msgctxt "BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBUILDUPPROGRESS.NAME"
msgid "{ELEMENT} build-up: {PERCENTAGE}"
msgstr "{ELEMENT}堆积：{PERCENTAGE}"

#. BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBUILDUPPROGRESS.TOOLTIP
msgctxt "BetterReef.STRINGS.MISC.STATUSITEMS.UNDERWATERVENTBUILDUPPROGRESS.TOOLTIP"
msgid "This geyser will become blocked when <style=\"KKeyword\">{ELEMENT}</style> build-up reaches 100%\n\nIt can be unblocked by building a <style=\"KKeyword\">Marine Drill</style> on top of the vent"
msgstr "当<style=\"KKeyword\">{ELEMENT}</style>堆积达到100%时，这个间歇泉会被阻挡\n\n可以在喷孔上建造<style=\"KKeyword\">海洋钻机</style>进行疏通"

